					<article id="post-30" class="post-30 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-php category-programming category-wordpress">
	<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title">
			<a href="http://bradkovach.com/2012/06/make-twitter-tools-respect-your-tweets/" title="Permalink to Make Twitter Tools respect your Tweets" rel="bookmark">Make Twitter Tools respect your Tweets</a>
		</h1>
	</header>
	<!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">

				
						
			<p>Twitter Tools is defacto Twitter-WordPress integration software, but it has one glitch that is easy to fix: tweet posts are formatted so horribly, it&#8217;s criminal.</p>
<p>By default Twitter Tools places the full text of a Tweet in post_content, and an abbreviated, ugly version of the tweet in post_title.  This is fine, because there are (usually, depending on your theme) formats for the proper display of a status.</p>
<p>Open twitter-tools.php.  After line 515, which reads</p><!-- Crayon Syntax Highlighter v2.6.1 -->

		<div id="crayon-53879388e63c5188692050" class="crayon-syntax crayon-theme-twilight crayon-font-consolas crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate" data-settings=" minimize scroll-mouseover" style=" width: 100%; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; float: none; clear: both; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;">
		
			<div class="crayon-toolbar" data-settings=" show" style="font-size: 12px !important;height: 18px !important; line-height: 18px !important;"><span class="crayon-title"></span>
			<div class="crayon-tools" style="font-size: 12px !important;height: 18px !important; line-height: 18px !important;"><div class="crayon-button crayon-nums-button" title="Toggle Line Numbers"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div><div class="crayon-button crayon-plain-button" title="Toggle Plain Code"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div><div class="crayon-button crayon-wrap-button" title="Toggle Line Wrap"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div><div class="crayon-button crayon-expand-button" title="Expand Code"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div><div class="crayon-button crayon-copy-button" title="Copy"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div><div class="crayon-button crayon-popup-button" title="Open Code In New Window"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div></div></div>
			<div class="crayon-info" style="min-height: 16.8px !important; line-height: 16.8px !important;"></div>
			<div class="crayon-plain-wrap"><textarea wrap="soft" class="crayon-plain print-no" data-settings="dblclick" readonly style="-moz-tab-size:4; -o-tab-size:4; -webkit-tab-size:4; tab-size:4; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;">
add_post_meta($post_id, 'aktt_twitter_id', $tweet-&gt;tw_id, true);</textarea></div>
			<div class="crayon-main" style="">
				<table class="crayon-table">
					<tr class="crayon-row">
				<td class="crayon-nums " data-settings="show">
					<div class="crayon-nums-content" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;"><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-53879388e63c5188692050-1">1</div></div>
				</td>
						<td class="crayon-code"><div class="crayon-pre" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;"><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-53879388e63c5188692050-1"><span class="crayon-e">add_post_meta</span><span class="crayon-sy">(</span><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-v">post_id</span><span class="crayon-sy">,</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-s">'aktt_twitter_id'</span><span class="crayon-sy">,</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-v">tweet</span><span class="crayon-o">-&gt;</span><span class="crayon-v">tw_id</span><span class="crayon-sy">,</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-t">true</span><span class="crayon-sy">)</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span></div></div></td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</div>
		</div>
<!-- [Format Time: 0.0011 seconds] -->
<p>type a new line that reads</p><!-- Crayon Syntax Highlighter v2.6.1 -->

		<div id="crayon-53879388e63dc524873193" class="crayon-syntax crayon-theme-twilight crayon-font-consolas crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate" data-settings=" minimize scroll-mouseover" style=" width: 100%; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; float: none; clear: both; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;">
		
			<div class="crayon-toolbar" data-settings=" show" style="font-size: 12px !important;height: 18px !important; line-height: 18px !important;"><span class="crayon-title"></span>
			<div class="crayon-tools" style="font-size: 12px !important;height: 18px !important; line-height: 18px !important;"><div class="crayon-button crayon-nums-button" title="Toggle Line Numbers"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div><div class="crayon-button crayon-plain-button" title="Toggle Plain Code"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div><div class="crayon-button crayon-wrap-button" title="Toggle Line Wrap"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div><div class="crayon-button crayon-expand-button" title="Expand Code"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div><div class="crayon-button crayon-copy-button" title="Copy"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div><div class="crayon-button crayon-popup-button" title="Open Code In New Window"><div class="crayon-button-icon"></div></div></div></div>
			<div class="crayon-info" style="min-height: 16.8px !important; line-height: 16.8px !important;"></div>
			<div class="crayon-plain-wrap"><textarea wrap="soft" class="crayon-plain print-no" data-settings="dblclick" readonly style="-moz-tab-size:4; -o-tab-size:4; -webkit-tab-size:4; tab-size:4; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;">
set_post_format($post_id, 'status');</textarea></div>
			<div class="crayon-main" style="">
				<table class="crayon-table">
					<tr class="crayon-row">
				<td class="crayon-nums " data-settings="show">
					<div class="crayon-nums-content" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;"><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-53879388e63dc524873193-1">1</div></div>
				</td>
						<td class="crayon-code"><div class="crayon-pre" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;"><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-53879388e63dc524873193-1"><span class="crayon-e">set_post_format</span><span class="crayon-sy">(</span><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-v">post_id</span><span class="crayon-sy">,</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-s">'status'</span><span class="crayon-sy">)</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span></div></div></td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</div>
		</div>
<!-- [Format Time: 0.0006 seconds] -->
<p>Next time Twitter Tools fetches tweets, it will format them as statuses.</p>
			
			</div>
